gobblin.data.management.convertion.hive

Class HiveConvertExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • gobblin.data.management.convertion.hive.HiveConvertExtractor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Extractor<Schema,QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity>, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public class HiveConvertExtractor
extends Object
implements Extractor<Schema,QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity>

    Extracts QueryBasedHiveConversionEntitys. A QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity can represent a hive table or a hive partition. Note that this extractor does not extract rows of a partition or a table. Entire table or partition is considered as a record.

    This extractor deserializes the HiveTable or HivePartition serialized by the HiveSource at HiveSource.HIVE_UNIT_SERIALIZED_KEY to build a QueryBasedHiveConversionEntity. Uses a HiveAvroSchemaProvider to get the avro Schema of the HiveTable or HivePartition being extracted.
